    "body": "Can confirm the behavior is the same in version 1.23.0.\n\nThe [documentation](https://starship.rs/config/#git-status) is pretty clear that deleted should only count deleted files **added to the staging area**:\n\n> deleted\tDisplays deleted when a file's deletion has been added to the staging area.\n",
